# 📘 Day 07 – Sets

This folder contains practice programs covering Python sets. These exercises demonstrate set creation, modification, mathematical operations, comprehensions, and practical applications.

---

## 📚 Concepts Covered

- Creating Sets
- Adding Elements
- Removing Elements
- Set Union
- Set Intersection
- Set Difference
- Symmetric Difference
- Membership Testing
- Removing Duplicates
- Finding Set Length
- Clearing Sets
- Frozen Sets
- Subsets & Supersets
- Set Comprehensions
- Practical Set Challenge

---

