## 🎯 Learning Outcomes

After completing these programs, I can:

- Create and modify sets
- Perform set operations
- Remove duplicate values efficiently
- Check membership
- Use frozen sets
- Compare subsets and supersets
- Write set comprehensions
- Solve practical problems using sets

